content:
A virtual private server (VPS) is a virtual machine sold as a service by an Internet hosting service. The virtual dedicated server (VDS) also has a similar meaning(More Information refers to Wikipedia).
Cancellation &amp; Refund STEP1: Login in BandwagonHost and move into Client Area.
STEP2: Find &ldquo;refund&rdquo; in the &ldquo;billing&rdquo; navigation, then submit cancellation&amp;refund request. {% asset_img fig1.png Fig1%}
STEP3: After clicking the button, BandwagonHost would automatically send an email to you to confirm your request. {% asset_img fig2.png Fig2: Your reply must ONLY contain &ldquo;I agree&rdquo;%}
STEP4: Waiting for 15-45 minutes, you would recieve an email containing the result. {% asset_img fig3.png Fig3: Succeed!%}
References BangwagonHost官网 BangwagonHost VPS搭建和配置
